{"tid":2215372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［痴撚線］［本土研］港共象徵式收$1續租粉嶺golf場三年 然後仲好意思話要至少6000億填人工島？","createTime":"2020-09-24T03:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:25:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8c9a012cd9ecffb9297a011f5ffbfce320fc82","tid":2215372,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGjkzOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGjkzOc.png&h=71675661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本土研究社 Liber Research Community<br />\n【粉嶺高球場批租竟賤上加賤】<br />\n<br />\n今日香港好彩重有盡責既北區區議員 袁浩倫 - 海袁 同未被DQ既記者識得追問，先發現原來政府又靜雞雞批多3年俾粉嶺高球場32公頃臨時續租，重要係變左收象徵性$1租短租租金，比起之前既私人遊樂場契約$1000地價加每3%更加賣大包。<br />\n<br />\n人地一個會藉可以賣到成幾千萬，你就話人地係非牟利用途所以只係收象徵性$1租，係「一貫做法」。又話財政緊縮唔夠錢派，另一方便就無敵賤租公有土地財產，咁點解唔立即收番做住過渡性房屋? 半年內起好立即大規模紓緩房屋問題啦。<br />\n<br />\n同埋一開始講話收番塊地用黎做公屋發展，今日最新既講法竟然變左係以「公營房屋作為重點」，即係好有可能收到之後就會有一塊塊拎去賣做豪宅既「其他重點」，政策修辭已經出現微妙變化。<br />\n<br />\n依家政府拖多3年既意思，亦好有可能3年之後又3年，其實林鄭即係話俾大家聽佢已經推左俾下屆特區政府發落，好明顯係玩緊「卸膀操」，唔駛佢任內處理。<br />\n<br />\n一日到黑係度講虛無飄緲既明日大嶼桂山島，明明眼前有塊地就繼續拖字決，林鄭妳重好意思推銷明日大嶼話「我們只欠土地」?<br />\n<br />\n#呢單野唔係我跟開<br />\n#3年之後又3年<br />\n#濫用短租政策<br />\n#繼續推動公地公用<br />\n#香港土地研究<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n【請政府交代粉嶺哥爾夫球場是否已獲秘密續約】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/3361136563982393/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F3361136563982393%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=c78a08cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/3361136563982393/</a><br />\n<br />\n【本研Podcast】（執波中）粉嶺哥爾夫球場遊記<br />\n🎧立即收聽：<a href=\"https://apple.co/3iflk1D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F3iflk1D&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=c497ae63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/3iflk1D</a><br />\n<br />\n－<br />\n🔥支持本土研究社研究工作：<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=603e1acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us/</a><br />\n🖥Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=19353f39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/</a><br />\n📸IG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/liberresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fliberresearch%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=d9bab96d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/liberresearch/</a><br />\n🖨TG: <a href=\"http://t.me/liberinfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fliberinfo&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=d85e8d65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/liberinfo</a><br />\n🎧 Podcast: <a href=\"https://apple.co/3ly0yfw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F3ly0yfw&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=79db5119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/3ly0yfw</a><br />\n🐦Twitter : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/LiberResearch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiberResearch&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=9c49df55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LiberResearch</a><br />\n🎥Youtube: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WOIKTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WOIKTk&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=5d48380d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WOIKTk</a><br />\n🧠研究義工報名申請表<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SbbyT3\" data-sr-url=\"https://